Package com.google.api.client.googleapis.extensions.servlet.subscriptions Description

com.google.api.client.util.Beta
Support for subscribing to topics and receiving notifications on servlet-based platforms.

Deprecated:(scheduled to be removed in 1.17) Use NotificationServlet or com.google.api.client.extensions.jdo.JdoDataStoreFactory with StoredChannel instead.
